{"id":42558,"date":"2024-01-16T19:09:45","date_gmt":"2024-01-16T13:39:45","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=42558"},"modified":"2023-02-16T19:09:49","modified_gmt":"2023-02-16T13:39:49","slug":"study-table-with-bookshelf-design","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/study-room-interiors\/study-table-with-bookshelf-design\/","title":{"rendered":"Study Table With Bookshelf Design Ideas: Double Up The Utility Of Your Home Office"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Bookshelf study table designs that will steal your heart and inspire you to remodel your home office.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Bread and butter. Autumn and orange. Laurel and Hardy. There is another equally iconic pairing \u2014 a study table with a bookshelf.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Hybrid spaces are the norm today, with our homes turning into offices. So, it makes sense to invest in study table bookshelf designs and get more bang for your buck. There is also the aspect of aesthetics \u2014 is there anything more gratifying than having a <em>dekho<\/em> at your books while taking a break from work or studies?&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>We often forget that having a study table and bookshelf together is a great decorating opportunity. Take a look at our expert-approved <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/study-room-interiors\/modern-study-table-designs\/\">modern study table<\/a> with bookshelf design ideas and find innovative ways to style your next home interiors project \u2014 whether it is to create a cosy corner for work or a platform to show off your enviable paperback collection.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">An Accent Wall Behind The Study Table With Bookshelf<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Don\u2019t play small with the wall behind the study table with bookshelf. You could add drama to the space with eye-catching wall paint or do what the pros do \u2014 highlight the wall with beautiful wallpaper. Your choice will peep from behind the wall-mounted bookshelf and make for a statement without being over the top.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/16181157\/Study-table-with-bookshelf-in-front-of-an-accent-wall.jpg\" alt=\"Study table with bookshelf in front of an accent wall\" class=\"wp-image-42568\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/16181157\/Study-table-with-bookshelf-in-front-of-an-accent-wall.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/16181157\/Study-table-with-bookshelf-in-front-of-an-accent-wall-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/16181157\/Study-table-with-bookshelf-in-front-of-an-accent-wall-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/16181157\/Study-table-with-bookshelf-in-front-of-an-accent-wall-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A wall that inspires fresh ideas<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Modern Study Table With Bookshelf Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>You will be spoilt for choice when it comes to modern study tables with bookshelf designs. There are many aspects to choose from \u2014 the study table, the material (wood, metal or acrylic), the chair, and what kind of bookshelf you would like to use with this setup. Choosing furniture has never been more exciting.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/16181148\/modern-study-table-with-bookshelf-design.jpg\" alt=\"Modern Study Table With Bookshelf Design\" class=\"wp-image-42567\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/16181148\/modern-study-table-with-bookshelf-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/16181148\/modern-study-table-with-bookshelf-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/16181148\/modern-study-table-with-bookshelf-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/16181148\/modern-study-table-with-bookshelf-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>You cannot go wrong with a modern study table<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Wall-Mounted Study Table With Bookshelf<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A wall-mounted study table with a bookshelf is a delight to the eyes. The clutter is kept at arm\u2019s length, the bookshelf draws up the eyes, and the under-desk area can accommodate baskets, bins, or under-table shelves for more storage.\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/16181142\/study-table-with-bookshelf-which-is-wall-mounted.jpg\" alt=\"Study table with bookshelf which is wall mounted\" class=\"wp-image-42566\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/16181142\/study-table-with-bookshelf-which-is-wall-mounted.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/16181142\/study-table-with-bookshelf-which-is-wall-mounted-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/16181142\/study-table-with-bookshelf-which-is-wall-mounted-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/16181142\/study-table-with-bookshelf-which-is-wall-mounted-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Mount it to the wall and free up the floor<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Corner Study Table With Bookshelf\u00a0<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Placing a corner study table with a bookshelf is a clever way to use those difficult-to-decorate nooks. You could add some plants to brighten up the area. Corner study tables also offer more privacy than rectangular study tables.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/16181136\/Study-table-with-bookshelf-placed-in-a-corner.jpg\" alt=\"Study table with bookshelf placed in a corner\" class=\"wp-image-42565\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/16181136\/Study-table-with-bookshelf-placed-in-a-corner.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/16181136\/Study-table-with-bookshelf-placed-in-a-corner-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/16181136\/Study-table-with-bookshelf-placed-in-a-corner-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/16181136\/Study-table-with-bookshelf-placed-in-a-corner-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Create a cosy work corner by the window<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Make your study room the perfect place for productivity\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/17141156\/make-your-study-room-the-perfect-place-for-productivity.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">L-Shaped Study Table With Bookshelf<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The L-shaped study table with bookshelf design presents a large surface area to store everything \u2014 from files and folders to stationery holders and decor pieces. This is suitable for all ages but ideal for those with a lot of paperwork and gadgets or even for siblings who study together or couples who work together.\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/16181130\/study-table-with-bookshelf-in-L-Shape.jpg\" alt=\"Study table with bookshelf in L-Shape\" class=\"wp-image-42564\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/16181130\/study-table-with-bookshelf-in-L-Shape.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/16181130\/study-table-with-bookshelf-in-L-Shape-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/16181130\/study-table-with-bookshelf-in-L-Shape-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/16181130\/study-table-with-bookshelf-in-L-Shape-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>An uber-chic L-shaped study table with a bookshelf<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Study Table With Bookshelf For Kids<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>While purchasing a study table with a bookshelf for kids, ensure the height of the table is conducive to them and they can reach the bookshelf easily. Also, aim for both these furniture pieces to be useful for a few more years to reduce waste.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/16181123\/A-study-table-with-bookshelf-for-kids.jpg\" alt=\"A study table with bookshelf for kids\" class=\"wp-image-42563\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/16181123\/A-study-table-with-bookshelf-for-kids.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/16181123\/A-study-table-with-bookshelf-for-kids-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/16181123\/A-study-table-with-bookshelf-for-kids-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/16181123\/A-study-table-with-bookshelf-for-kids-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Match the study table height to the kids<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Study Table With Bookshelf Design That Has Extra Drawers<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Having multiple drawers is a boon for the owners. Extra storage space always improves the functionality of the piece and is helpful as much for storing everyday essentials as the extra chargers and wires.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/16181116\/A-study-table-with-bookshelf-design-that-has-extra-drawers.jpg\" alt=\"A study table with bookshelf design that has extra drawers\" class=\"wp-image-42562\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/16181116\/A-study-table-with-bookshelf-design-that-has-extra-drawers.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/16181116\/A-study-table-with-bookshelf-design-that-has-extra-drawers-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/16181116\/A-study-table-with-bookshelf-design-that-has-extra-drawers-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/16181116\/A-study-table-with-bookshelf-design-that-has-extra-drawers-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>The joy of multiple drawers in a workspace<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Study Table With Overhead Bookshelf<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>An overhead bookshelf is an excellent option for those who are space-deprived. Small apartments and tiny studies benefit from going vertical with bookshelves as they create visual interest while keeping the room clutter-free. If placed next to a window, even better for they provide respite during breaks.\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/16181110\/study-table-with-overhead-bookshelf.jpg\" alt=\"Study table with overhead bookshelf\" class=\"wp-image-42561\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/16181110\/study-table-with-overhead-bookshelf.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/16181110\/study-table-with-overhead-bookshelf-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/16181110\/study-table-with-overhead-bookshelf-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/16181110\/study-table-with-overhead-bookshelf-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Look up at that overhead bookshelf<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Study Table With Floor-Level Bookshelf<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>It helps to think out of the box. Instead of keeping everything eye-level and vertical, a quirky addition to a room is a floor-level bookshelf that can also double up as a seating area. Apart from being versatile, it is stylish and unique.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/16181104\/study-table-with-floor-level-bookshelf.jpg\" alt=\"A study table with floor-level bookshelf\" class=\"wp-image-42560\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/16181104\/study-table-with-floor-level-bookshelf.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/16181104\/study-table-with-floor-level-bookshelf-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/16181104\/study-table-with-floor-level-bookshelf-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/16181104\/study-table-with-floor-level-bookshelf-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A versatile bookshelf that doubles up as seating<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Vintage-Edition Study Table With Bookshelf Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Why are we sticking just to modern, industrial and mid-century study tables with bookshelves? A vintage study table or chair will add charm to your space in no time and add another layer of sophistication to the aesthetics.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/16181057\/Study-table-with-bookshelf-design-in-a-vintage-style.jpg\" alt=\"Study table with bookshelf design in a vintage style\" class=\"wp-image-42559\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/16181057\/Study-table-with-bookshelf-design-in-a-vintage-style.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/16181057\/Study-table-with-bookshelf-design-in-a-vintage-style-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/16181057\/Study-table-with-bookshelf-design-in-a-vintage-style-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/16181057\/Study-table-with-bookshelf-design-in-a-vintage-style-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Vintage validation for a charming work corner<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Study tables with bookshelf designs can transform any space into a serene oasis. Do remember functionality and aesthetics can be balanced \u2014 one doesn\u2019t have to be sacrificed for another. Using built-in bookshelves will free up space to add other elements to your room. And yes, bookshelves aren\u2019t just for books \u2014 showcase your collectables, plants and figurines apart from your literary collection. Here\u2019s to the timeless delights of reading and working in beautiful spaces!<\/p>\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Productive Spaces For An Ideal Home<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Smart modular solutions for Indian homes<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/>\n        <!-- <span class=\"sales-txt-label\" id=\"labeltxt\">Enter your name*<\/span>  -->\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"form-row dc-falg-row\">\n        <!-- <div class=\"form-group col-md-3 guideForm\">\n            <select name=\"your-phone-ext\" id=\"id_select2_example\" class=\"id_select2_example drop-downfield form-dropdown\"\n                onfocus='this.size=5;' onblur='this.size=1;' onchange='this.size=1; this.blur();'\n                data-width=\"100%\" data-minimum-results-for-search=\"Infinity\">\n               \n                <option value=\"+01\"\n                    data-img_src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06163948\/01.png\">\n                    +01\n                <\/option>\n                <option value=\"+91\"\n                    data-img_src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06164015\/91.png\"\n                    selected>\n                    +91\n                <\/option>\n                <option value=\"+44\"\n                    data-img_src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06163955\/44.png\">\n                    +44\n                <\/option>\n                <option value=\"+61\"\n                    data-img_src=\"https:\/\/media.